      "description": "The WisdomTree High Income Laddered Municipal Fund (WTMY) is an exchange-traded fund that mostly invests in broad credit fixed income. The fund aims to provide federal tax-exempt current income through an actively managed portfolio of US municipal bonds with varying credit ratings. The fund seeks to maintain an average portfolio duration between five and ten years. WTMY was launched on Apr 3, 2025 and is issued by WisdomTree.",
